reviewText: WB is a fine pianist and educator. His three volume set supplies the self-motivated, intermediate pianist with enough instruction in jazz theory, reharmonization, improvisation, comping, soloing, etc., to last a lifetime. Given the various costs of private lessons, a bargain at many times the price.
The "Bomb" is a slang term meaning something is good, great, excellent, superb, and that's what this DVD is all the above.
